title: 12/28/21 DPS Hour 1   Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 12/28/21 DPS Hour 1   Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
description:
Rob and TJ take up for James Harden and how he has adjusted his game with the Nets this season given the new rules. The guys break down the Lakers' season to this point and the issues they have had with star guard Russell Westbrook. Reacting to Pete Carroll saying his team doesn't need a rebuild, the guys have a spirited debate about what the Seahawks should do from here.
